# Environment variable example

Create a file named `.env` at the repository root (it should NOT be committed) and add your Unsplash API key like this:

UNSPLASH_API_KEY=your_unsplash_api_key_here

Do NOT commit your real .env file. This repository includes a server (server.js) that reads the key from process.env.UNSPLASH_API_KEY and proxies requests from the client to Unsplash so the key stays on the server.
